## Troubleshooting

### "LLM API key not set"
- Check `OPENROUTER_API_KEY` is in `.env` (not commented out)
- Key should start with `sk-or-v1-` (OpenRouter format)
- Restart backend after updating `.env`

### "Vector search unavailable"
- This is OK if ChromaDB not running
- Backend will fall back to MongoDB-only mode
- To enable: `chroma run --path ./chroma_data`

### "MongoDB connection refused"
- Ensure MongoDB is running: `mongo` or `mongosh`
- Check `MONGO_URI` matches your MongoDB setup
- Default: `mongodb://localhost:27017`

### "Port 3001 already in use"
- Change `PORT` environment variable
- Or kill process: `lsof -ti:3001 | xargs kill -9`

