## OpenRouter Model Selection Guide

### Budget-Conscious (Recommended for POC)
```env
LLM_MODEL=qwen/qwen3.5-397b-a17b
LLM_BASE_URL=https://openrouter.ai/api/v1
```
- **Cost**: ~$0.1 per 1M tokens
- **Speed**: Very fast
- **Quality**: Good for oceanographic QA
- **Use Case**: Production, demos

### Highest Quality
```env
LLM_MODEL=openai/gpt-4-turbo
LLM_BASE_URL=https://openrouter.ai/api/v1
```
- **Cost**: ~$10 per 1M tokens
- **Speed**: Moderate
- **Quality**: Excellent reasoning
- **Use Case**: Complex analysis, research

### Open Source Option
```env
LLM_MODEL=meta-llama/llama-2-70b
LLM_BASE_URL=https://openrouter.ai/api/v1
```
- **Cost**: ~$0.7 per 1M tokens
- **Speed**: Moderate
- **Quality**: Good
- **Use Case**: Privacy-conscious deployments

